In collaboration with digital collage artist, Slimesunday, we present: 

“That's Nifty”

a podcast that features a prominent digital artist and his two run of the mill NFT (Non-Fungible Token) collectors interviewing figures in the NFT Art space.  They don't always know what is going on, but they know it's nifty. Moments captured here will document the rising tide surrounding the NFT Space as it enters the zeitgeist.

Twitter/Instagram: @ThatsNFT

Hosts:
@slimesunday
@CryptoKitch
@TNobel33

No Rival Network is a collection of podcasts dedicated to educating, promoting and advocating for the world of esports. Catch up on all the latest competitive esports news across the globe, hear from experts and personalities on contemporary esports topics, and join in destigmatizing gaming while instead promoting its positive effects.

